Button types

Source: vignettes/button_types.Rmd
button_types.Rmd

Here you may find preset Bootstrap button types. For more information, see bsplus::bs_button().

Please, refer to the Customizing buttons with css vignette for tips on how to further customize the buttons. 


library(downloadthis)

Default

mtcars %>%
  download_this(
    output_name = "mtcars dataset",
    output_extension = ".csv",
    button_label = "Download data as csv",
    button_type = "default",
    has_icon = TRUE,
    icon = "fa fa-save"
  )

Primary

mtcars %>%
  download_this(
    output_name = "mtcars dataset",
    output_extension = ".xlsx",
    button_label = "Download data as xlsx",
    button_type = "primary",
    has_icon = TRUE,
    icon = "fa fa-save"
  )
